      <title>特朗普的“文化捍卫者”将重塑司法部民权部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/trump-s-culture-defender-set-to-remake-doj-civil-rights-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[司法部民权部门几十年来一直致力于保护种族、民族、宗教少数群体以及妇女的权利——这些群体是美国非法歧视的最常见受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/trump-s-culture-defender-set-to-remake-doj-civil-rights-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
