    <item>
      <title>规模虽小但至关重要的金属市场急于适应中国的打压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/tiny-but-vital-metal-markets-rush-to-adjust-to-chinese-clampdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对三种稀缺金属出口的限制已经让市场感到不安。现在，更大规模的打击似乎将对美国国防和芯片制造业的供应链产生深远影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/tiny-but-vital-metal-markets-rush-to-adjust-to-chinese-clampdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚将在主要政党重新加入对话后恢复联合政府谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/romania-to-resume-coalition-talks-after-key-party-rejoins-dialog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚最大的执政党搁置了最近的一场争端，之后其亲欧政党正在恢复谈判，以组建新政府并阻止极右翼势力掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/romania-to-resume-coalition-talks-after-key-party-rejoins-dialog</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:24:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从也门发射的火箭弹击中特拉维夫地区；16 人受轻伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/rocket-fired-from-yemen-strikes-an-area-of-tel-aviv-overnight-16-people-lightly-injured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列特拉维夫（美联社）——以色列军方周六称，一枚从也门发射的火箭弹夜间击中特拉维夫地区，造成 16 人被碎玻璃伤。几天前，以色列空袭袭击了胡塞叛军，这些叛军一直在发射导弹声援加沙的巴勒斯坦人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/rocket-fired-from-yemen-strikes-an-area-of-tel-aviv-overnight-16-people-lightly-injured</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 07:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥学区首席执行官因市长与工会冲突被解雇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/chicago-education-board-fires-ceo-pedro-martinez-after-union-mayor-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会周五采取了一项非同寻常的举措，解雇了该学区的首席执行官佩德罗·马丁内斯 (Pedro Martinez)，这是马丁内斯与市长之间长达数月的争执的一个戏剧性进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/chicago-education-board-fires-ceo-pedro-martinez-after-union-mayor-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 03:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登签署美国支出协议以避免政府关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-passes-plan-to-fund-government-as-shutdown-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登签署了拨款法案，以确保美国政府运转至 3 月中旬，避免年底关闭政府，并将未来的支出决定权交由唐纳德·特朗普担任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-passes-plan-to-fund-government-as-shutdown-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 23:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
